text: Malia Ann Obama (born July 4, 1998) is the elder daughter of the 44th president of the United States Barack Obama and Michelle Obama. == Early life == Malia Ann Obama was born at University of Chicago Medical Center on July 4, 1998, as the elder of two daughters to Barack Obama and Michelle Obama. She was delivered by her parents' friend and physician Anita Blanchard. Her younger sister is Sasha Obama. Obama and her sister were named two of "The Most Influential Teens of 2014" by TIME magazine. == Career == Obama made her television debut in a 2008 episode of Access Hollywood. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people
title: Malia Obama
